* print bottle
  + bottle count
  - print
    - concat
      + bottle count
      + text
        ! bottles of beer on the wall,
      + endline

* throw bottle
  + bottle count
  - if
    + not equals
      + bottle count
      + number
        ! 0
    - print bottle
      + bottle count
    - throw bottle
      + subtract
        + bottle count
        + number
          ! 1

* main
  - throw bottle
    + number
      ! 99

- main
